h2 Hi #{@user.name}!

- if @apps.size > 0
  table.table.table-striped
    thead
      th Name
      th Status
      th Aufgabe
      th Tests passed?
      th Reviewed?
      th Punkte
      th Links
    tbody
      - @apps.each do |app|
        tr class=app_status_class(app)
          td= link_to_if app.ready?, app.name, user_app_path(app.user, app)
          td= app_status(app)
          td= app.exercise_id
          td= app_tests_passed_icon(app)
          td= app_review_icon(app)
          td= app_points(app)
          td
            - if app.ready?
              = link_to 'Edit', edit_user_app_path(app.user, app), class: 'btn btn-primary'
              = link_to 'Open', app.public_url, target: :blank, class: 'btn btn-default'
              = link_to 'Logs', user_app_logs_path(app.user, app), class: 'btn btn-default'
              = link_to 'Jenkins', app.jenkins_url, class: 'btn btn-default', target: '_blank'
            - else
              | Deine App wird gerade im Hintergrund aktualisiert. Wenn dies l√§nger als 5 Minuten
                dauert solltest du dich melden: <a href="mailto:igelmund@htw-berlin.de">igelmund@htw-berlin.de</a>.
    tfoot
      tr
        td colspan=8
          h4 Gesamtpunkte: #{@user.total_points}

- else
  p You currently have no app configured.

= link_to 'Create a new app!', new_user_app_path(current_user), class: 'btn btn-primary'
